subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which Rajput dynasty ruled Jaipur during the medieval period?
question_hi: जैसेंट मध्येतर सम्पर्करण किसेंट के वर्ग का क्या जैसेंट मध्येतर सम्पर्करण की संगूणी वर्ग मध्येतर सम्पर्करण के बन्देगुणी वर्ग की संगूणी वर्गियांगूणी वर्ग
explanation_en: During the medieval period, the Banاجاani sangunani vaarg had control over Jaipur. The Banagaani sangunani vaarg was a prominent Rajput clan that ruled Jaipur and its surrounding areas.

subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which Rajput dynasty ruled Jaipur from 1728 to 1803 AD?
explanation_en: The Banagaani sangunani vaarg of the Marwar-Jaisalmer dynasty ruled Jaipur from 1728 AD to 1803 AD.

subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king was the founder of Jodhpur?
explanation_en: Prince Maharaja Umaid Singh was the founder of Jodhpur. He founded the Umaid Bhawan palace, which is a major tourist attraction in Jodhpur.
